Nuvama on Bajaj Cons

Buy, TP Rs 435

Management meet Key insights

i) Targets double-digit revenue growth (17.5% in 9MFY26) with mid to high single-digit growth in ADHO portfolio (double-digit volume growth in Q3FY26);

ii) EBITDA margin to gradually expand to early twenties (17.2% in 9MFY26);

iii) Direct distribution reach to expand to ~0.9mn outlets, up ~10% annually over the next 4–5 years;

iv) Copra price correction could aid coconut oil promotions/margins in FY27;

v) Banjara posted double-digit growth with mid-teen margins.
